00:09:40,708 --> 00:09:41,889
takes time to vest.

224
00:09:41,889 --> 00:09:44,132
So are they immediately entitled to this money,

225
00:09:44,132 --> 00:09:45,473
this rev share when the game comes out?

226
00:09:45,473 --> 00:09:47,575
Or do they have to have earned it by working for the game

227
00:09:47,575 --> 00:09:49,617
for a certain amount of time?

228
00:09:49,617 --> 00:09:52,700
You need to think about which platforms are covered.

229
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:56,744
If they're working on the Steam version and you think maybe it'll be on console later

230
00:09:56,744 --> 00:09:59,968
