00:10:10,623 --> 00:10:13,324
Speaking of scope, you also need to have

236
00:10:13,324 --> 00:10:16,566
a written statement of work that describes

237
00:10:16,566 --> 00:10:18,667
the scope of work, what someone is delivering to you.

