00:10:27,212 --> 00:10:27,873
for you to pay.

244
00:10:29,090 --> 00:10:32,772
And if you're not satisfied or honestly if you need to cancel

245
00:10:32,772 --> 00:10:36,315
the game, there needs to be a clear right for the developer

246
00:10:36,315 --> 00:10:39,216
to terminate. You don't want to be obligated to pay people for

247
00:10:39,216 --> 00:10:41,858
work you don't need. And then you're going to need to think

248
00:10:41,858 --> 00:10:43,899
about what happens when you terminate them. Are you going

249
00:10:43,899 --> 00:10:46,801
to pay them? Look over these things. That can lead to a big

